6-1回答问题api的实现
php artisan make:migration create_table_answers --create=answers
php artisan migrate --pretend
php artisan migrate:rollback

新建answer model
php artisan make:model Answer







7-1评论API的实现
php artisan make:migration create_table_comments --create=comments
php artisan migrate --pretend

新建comment model
php artisan make:model Comment
php artisan migrate





8-1通用API的实现
php artisan make:migration create_table_answer_user --create=answer_user
php artisan migrate --pretend
php artisan migrate




